    "id": "14",
    "title": "Merge K Sorted Lists",
    "difficulty": "Hard",
    "description": "You are given an array of k linked-lists lists, each linked-list is sorted in ascending order. Merge all the linked-lists into one sorted linked-list and return it. (Input uses arrays to represent lists)\n\nInput Format:\nFirst line: integer k (number of lists)\nNext k lines: The first integer is the size of the list, followed by the space-separated elements.",
    "examples": [
      {
        "input": "3\n3 1 4 5\n3 1 3 4\n2 2 6",
